<!-- S2: TAPE MACHINE -->
<section class="hidden" id="s2">
<div class="section-label">02 · MAGNETIC MEMORY</div>
<div class="section-title">Tape Machine Explorer</div>
<div class="section-sub">Two-inch 24-track tape at 30 ips — the professional standard. As the oxide-coated tape passes over three heads (erase, record, playback), magnetic particles align to the audio signal's waveform. Speed governs high-frequency response; width governs dynamic range.</div>
