<div class="section-title">Console Signal Routing</div>
<div class="section-sub">SSL 4000, Neve 8078, API 1604 — each console has a distinct sonic DNA rooted in its transformer topology, capacitor choices, and summing bus architecture. Signal enters a mic preamp, routes through EQ and dynamics, collects on group buses, and sums to stereo.</div>
